== Remote Participation ==

According to the [http://lists.ffii.org/pipermail/board-minutes/2005-November/000001.html board decsion of 2005-11-19], the [:FfiiKonvAgenda0511En: agenda] is fixed one week in advance and active members can [:FfiiKonvPoll0511En: give a non-binding vote].

== Audio streaming ==

You will be able to listen to the General Assembly remotely via the [:FfiiKonvStream0511En: audio streaming of the conference].

== Side events ==

 * Champagne for Creativity lunch tuesday 12:00-14:00 in Rennaissance Hotel; status: booked, invitations sent out, a substantial number of parliamentarians is coming
 * Dinner & Party tuesday 18-24.00, announcement of European for the Year election result 21:00; status: booked

